{
  "stem": "13141.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And to make a long story short, he said, all right.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He said, I give you a job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You will not make very much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But you could carry luggage at the airport.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he-- they, they paid me a little money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I went to the airport every day, and I carried luggage.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then my friend, that Herbert Dreyfuss, he told me, when-- once you land in Spain, send me a telegram what I could bring, you know.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I asked them in Spain, I mean, what-- you know, what you can sell here, convert into money?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I couldn't believe, they'd say-- I mean, I could only bring something you could get in Germany, you know?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they told me fountain pens, which I told back, that's out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they told me, horseradish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Horseradish?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Just like the way you hear it, horseradish, the, the plants, the roots-- Mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I sent him a telegram-- to Herbert.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From Spain, there was no problem for me to send a telegram.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I sent it from the Lufthansa office.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They sent telegrams there all day long, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I sent him a telegram.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, landed safely.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Bring as much horseradish as you can.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He thought I, I must have gone wacky, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So a few days later, maybe three or four days later, or five days later, he arrived.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he checked in there with the Lufthansa.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I told them at the Lufthansa when he come, they should tell me-- my friend.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we were two.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we-- he, he also carried luggage.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The two of us carried luggage.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But then the, the flights stopped coming from, from Munich.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this was also reason that this-- the third fellow couldn't get out, the Lothar Levine.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
